+------+---------------+----------+--------------+--------+-----------------+-------+-----------+-------+--------+------------+-------------+
|    2 | SUBQUERY      | products | NULL         | ALL    | NULL            | NULL  | NULL      | NULL  |   9836 |      10    | Using where |
+------+---------------+----------+--------------+--------+-----------------+-------+-----------+-------+--------+------------+-------------+

## Column Selectivity:
